{"tid":1250330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張弛抗高牆 以無法為有法","createTime":"2019-06-22T04:46:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T04:46:38.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b2d930fdcf5a8310b38bdb55b56d2b07b37f5c19","tid":1250330,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:46:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190622/20710691\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190622%2F20710691&d=Hh5C2Wm8JWR9usSbwEl%2Bh8kuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=e9405446\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190622%2F20710691&h=bd480b71\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190622/20710691</a><br />\n<br />\n張弛抗高牆 以無法為有法<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190622/large/a0401a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190622%2Flarge%2Fa0401a.gif&h=3c62485f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n示威者上午近11時佔領夏慤道，交通癱瘓。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【反送中】<br />\n<br />\n這一夜，雞蛋擲高牆，灣仔警察總部吞蛋無數。<br />\n<br />\n外媒形容香港的示威者正在進化。昨日港人就放棄過去遊行、靜坐、佔領的定式，實行「Be Water」，由政總開始，流動到警察總部，再發展出多個支流，導致稅務大樓、入境事務大樓等多個政府辦公室停擺。<br />\n<br />\n氣氛有時緊張，有時平靜。人們的訴求則始終如一：撤回送中條例、平反暴動指控、釋放被捕人士、嚴懲6.12濫用武力警務人員。<br />\n<br />\n入夜後，過萬人又在警總、金鐘匯流。無形，無式，無從控制。<br />\n<br />\n記者︰關冠麒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190622/large/a0401b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190622%2Flarge%2Fa0401b.gif&h=b2ed4fbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190622/large/a0401c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190622%2Flarge%2Fa0401c.gif&h=7e474f22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n眾志秘書長黃之鋒號召包圍警總，持咪高峰的警方談判專家中午出現，甫開聲即被噓走。雷釗河攝<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190622/large/a0401d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190622%2Flarge%2Fa0401d.gif&h=7482463b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n下午1時許，有人向警總高牆上的警徽掟雞蛋，其他人勸阻。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190622/large/a0401e.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190622%2Flarge%2Fa0401e.gif&h=b82846a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有警員制服沾上蛋液。<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190622/large/a0401f.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190622%2Flarge%2Fa0401f.gif&h=36a74146&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一輛警車一度在警總外被困。<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190622/large/a0401g.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190622%2Flarge%2Fa0401g.gif&h=fa0d41d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n下午2時許，大批手持雨傘示威者一度衝擊警總夏愨公園大門。<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190622/large/a0401h.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190622%2Flarge%2Fa0401h.gif&h=232d5374&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n示威者一度嘗試衝入警察總部，最終沒有成功。<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190622/large/a0401i.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190622%2Flarge%2Fa0401i.gif&h=ef8753ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n示威者晚上再向警總掟蛋，警察手持盾牌在警總門前戒備。王心義攝<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190622/large/a0401j.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190622%2Flarge%2Fa0401j.gif&h=61085409&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警察總部軍器廠街側門晚上被示威者封鎖。<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190622/large/a0401k.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190622%2Flarge%2Fa0401k.gif&h=ada25497&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n過萬人至深夜仍包圍警察總部，聲勢浩大。<br />\n <br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n便衣警拒出示委任證惹不滿<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n艱苦也義無反顧 老嫩一齊行"}]}